  ('SS-G3-EDM-SCO3', 'SS-G3-EDM-ELO1', 'SS-G3-EDM', 'SS', 'social-studies', 'G3', '3', 'Economic Decision Making', '3-EDM-V1-Appreciate that major economic activities of agriculture and tourism are linked to the natural resources of our island ', 2279, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:23.983713+00:00'),
