  ('LANG-G4-LS-SCO18', 'LANG-G4-LS-ELO1', 'LANG-G4-LS', 'LANG', 'language-arts', 'G4', '4', 'Listening and Speaking', 'give constructive oral feedback using prompts such as “I notice...I wonder...” when responding to classmates'' presentations or ideas. ', 2621, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:24.495614+00:00'),
