  ('LANG-G4-LS-SCO27', 'LANG-G4-LS-ELO1', 'LANG-G4-LS', 'LANG', 'language-arts', 'G4', '4', 'Listening and Speaking', 'identify, share, and analyze culturally relevant songs, calypso, soca, drama, and poetry with fluency, rhythm, and pace for literal and subtle purpose and meaning  ', 2630, '[]'::jsonb, '2026-02-21T17:24:24.495614+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G4-LS-SCO28', 'LANG-G4-LS-ELO1', 'LANG-G4-LS', 'LANG', 'language-arts', 'G4', '4', 'Listening and Speaking', 'further develop meaningful oral language use and conventions of oral language(s) as appropriate to the context and purpose: 
•	word order
